  "description": {
    "en": "A classic cocktail featuring gin, lemon juice, orange curaçao, and dry vermouth. It offers a complex balance of citrus, floral, and herbal notes.",
    "zh": "一款經典雞尾酒，包含琴酒、檸檬汁、橙味庫拉索和乾苦艾酒。它提供了柑橘、花香和草本風味的複雜平衡。"
  },
  "historical_reference": {
    "en": "**Origin:** This cocktail first appeared in the early 20th century.\n\n*   Attributed to Harry Craddock, though variations exist.\n*   Evolved from simpler gin-based drinks.\n*   Gained popularity during the Prohibition era.",
    "zh": "**起源：** 這款雞尾酒最早出現在 20 世紀初。\n\n*   歸功於哈利·克拉多克，但存在變體。\n*   從更簡單的琴酒飲料演變而來。\n*   在禁酒時期廣受歡迎。"
  },
  "technique": {
    "en": "Shake all ingredients with ice and strain into a chilled glass.",
    "zh": "將所有材料與冰塊搖勻，然後濾入冰鎮的玻璃杯中。"
